すべての実装されたインタフェース:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,V>, DeepCloneable, ICollection<K,V>
@Deprecated public class CollectionStrictSync<K,V> extends CollectionSync<K,V>
推奨されていません。
high maintenance cost
CollectionSync but all methods are synchronized. The lock is shared across all methods.
It may cause huge lags when doing large operations.
